  <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 12px;">ScarCruft's 'Ruby Jumper': North Korea Is Using Zoho WorkDrive to Bridge Air-Gapped Networks</h1>
  <p style="color: #555; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px;">North Korean state hackers used a legitimate cloud platform as their covert command channel — and added a USB relay to reach systems that have no internet connection at all.</p>
